# ğŸ¤– Robot Mobile Charging Station Mini Program

A **WeChat Mini Program** for monitoring and controlling **mobile robot charging stations**, built with **uni-app (Vue 3)** and **uniCloud (Alibaba Cloud)**.

The project adopts a **frontendâ€“backend decoupled, device-agnostic architecture**, enabling seamless evolution from **UI mock development** to **cloud-based simulation** and ultimately **real robot integration**, without major frontend changes.

---

## ğŸš€ Tech Stack

* **Frontend**: uni-app + Vue 3 (`<script setup>`)
* **Cloud Backend**: uniCloud (Alibaba Cloud)
* **Database**: uniCloud Cloud Database
* **Platform**: WeChat Mini Program

---

## ğŸ§© Architecture Overview

This project follows a **layered architecture**:

```text
Frontend (Mini Program)
  â”œâ”€ UI Pages (Robot List / Detail / Control)
  â”œâ”€ Service Layer (API abstraction)
  â†“
Cloud Backend (uniCloud)
  â”œâ”€ Cloud Functions (business APIs)
  â”œâ”€ Cloud Database (robot state & commands)
  â†“
Device Layer (Future)
  â”œâ”€ Real robots via HTTP / MQTT
```

* **Frontend** focuses on UI and interaction only
* **Backend** provides unified data and command APIs
* **Device layer** can be replaced or extended without affecting the Mini Program

