## ğŸ—„ï¸ Data Model (Overview)

The system uses a cloud-based data model to simulate and support real robot operations:

* `robots` â€” robot base information
* `telemetry_latest` â€” latest robot status (battery, position, online)
* `faults` â€” fault and error records
* `commands` â€” control command records

This design supports **real-time monitoring and auditable control workflows**, even before physical robots are available.

